WEBVTT

00:10.167 --> 00:11.298
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON GREENLEAF.</i>

00:11.300 --> 00:12.865
HERE'S WHAT THE
FEDS THINK HAPPENED.

00:12.867 --> 00:15.732
JACOB TRANSFERRED
$200,000 OF CHURCH FUNDS

00:15.734 --> 00:18.265
INTO WHAT TURNED OUT
TO BE A PERSONAL ACCOUNT,

00:18.267 --> 00:20.399
AND THEN YOU WITHDREW
ALL THAT MONEY

00:20.401 --> 00:21.865
TO PAY OFF THE IRS.

00:21.867 --> 00:24.165
I'VE CALLED AN EMERGENCY MEETING
OF THE DEACON BOARD

00:24.167 --> 00:25.698
TO DISCUSS YOUR REMOVAL.

00:25.700 --> 00:27.499
AND WHO WILL YOU
GET TO PREACH HERE?

00:27.501 --> 00:28.832
PHILIP DEMARS!

00:28.834 --> 00:30.398
HARMONY AND HOPE
MINISTRIES.

00:30.400 --> 00:32.031
IS THAT THE MONEY
BISHOP GAVE YOU?

00:32.033 --> 00:33.098
NONE OF
YOUR DAMN BUSINESS.

00:33.100 --> 00:34.265
THAT'S WHAT
WE'RE GONNA LIVE ON

00:34.267 --> 00:36.465
ONCE WE CROSS THAT OL'
LITTLE BORDER TO MEXICO.

00:36.467 --> 00:38.065
TASHA IS OUR ONLY
WAY OUT OF THIS.

00:38.067 --> 00:39.899
SHE LOVES YOU, JACOB.
WHERE DOES THAT LEAVE ME?

00:39.901 --> 00:41.165
JACOB!

00:41.167 --> 00:42.999
ARE YOU OKAY TO TALK
TO THE FBI TONIGHT?

00:43.001 --> 00:45.598
YES.
I WANT A DIVORCE, JACOB.

00:45.600 --> 00:47.498
[ DOOR OPENS ]

00:47.500 --> 00:49.231
IS LIONEL
MY FATHER OR NOT?

00:49.233 --> 00:50.432
I DON'T KNOW.

00:50.434 --> 00:52.865
YOU'LL NEVER STOP
FIGHTING TO SAVE US ALL.

00:52.867 --> 00:54.065
MY PRECIOUS DAUGHTER.

00:54.067 --> 00:58.531
GOD'S GREAT DAY
OF RECKONING IS ANY DAY

00:58.533 --> 01:03.399
THAT YOU SAY, "THANK YOU, JESUS,
AND TAKE WHAT'S YOURS."

01:03.401 --> 01:04.899
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

01:04.901 --> 01:06.698
YOU KILLED MY DAD!

01:06.700 --> 01:07.965
I DIDN'T MEAN TO DO IT!

01:07.967 --> 01:09.898
BE READY TO DIE, BISHOP.

01:09.900 --> 01:11.999
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

01:12.001 --> 01:18.798
♪♪

01:18.800 --> 01:21.865
OKAY.

01:21.867 --> 01:23.965
I KNOW YOU'RE UPSET BUT YOU HAVE
GOT TO SEE THE FIRST LADY --

01:23.967 --> 01:24.965
[ GASPS, CRIES ]

01:24.967 --> 01:26.698
WAIT! NO! NO!

01:26.700 --> 01:28.765
COME ON, BISHOP.
NO, DON'T!

01:28.767 --> 01:30.265
BLOOD IS ON YOUR HANDS, BISHOP.
COME ON!

01:30.267 --> 01:33.665
KARINE, DON'T CALL THE POLICE.
YOU GO.

01:33.667 --> 01:35.465
JUST GO!

01:35.467 --> 01:39.865
[ SOBBING ]

01:39.867 --> 01:42.598
OOH, BISHOP.

01:42.600 --> 01:45.465
YOU GOT SOME
AMAZING FAITH HERE.

01:45.467 --> 01:47.299
SHAME IT'S MISPLACED.

01:47.301 --> 01:48.965
NO.

01:48.967 --> 01:51.298
NO, IT'S NOT.

01:51.300 --> 01:54.898
YOU'RE NOT
A KILLER, BASIE.

01:54.900 --> 01:57.965
YOU DIDN'T KNOW THAT UNTIL
RIGHT NOW, DID YOU, SON?

01:57.967 --> 02:04.231
♪♪

02:04.233 --> 02:05.965
♪ AMEN ♪

02:05.967 --> 02:08.432
♪♪

02:08.434 --> 02:09.698
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

02:09.700 --> 02:11.098
♪ AMEN ♪

02:11.100 --> 02:13.932
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

02:13.934 --> 02:16.598
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

02:16.600 --> 02:19.665
♪♪

02:19.667 --> 02:20.932
♪ WELL ♪

02:20.934 --> 02:24.465
♪♪

02:24.467 --> 02:27.398
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

02:27.400 --> 02:32.998
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

02:33.000 --> 02:36.065
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

02:36.067 --> 02:39.465
♪♪

02:39.467 --> 02:41.265
♪ YEAH ♪

02:41.267 --> 02:44.265
-- Captions by VITAC --
 www.vitac.com

02:44.267 --> 02:47.265
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

02:47.267 --> 02:51.865
♪♪

02:51.867 --> 02:53.998
OOH, WELL NOT EVEN
PETER COULD DENY

02:54.000 --> 02:55.332
WHAT JUST HAPPENED
UP IN THERE, MAE.

02:55.334 --> 02:56.665
WHAT DO YOU THINK
JUST HAPPENED?

02:56.667 --> 02:58.332
GIRLFRIEND,
YOU GOT YOURSELF A CHURCH!

02:58.334 --> 03:00.265
LADY MAE! LADY MAE!
WHAT?

03:00.267 --> 03:01.798
THE BISHOP, BASIE --
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:01.800 --> 03:06.298
HE'S GOT A GUN.
I THINK HE'S GONNA SHOOT BISHOP.

03:06.300 --> 03:11.198
GO IN PEACE
AND SERVE THE LORD.

03:11.200 --> 03:16.565
♪♪

03:16.567 --> 03:20.265
YOU DO THE SAME.

03:20.267 --> 03:26.465
♪♪

03:26.467 --> 03:32.532
♪♪

03:32.534 --> 03:34.532
[ MOANS ]

03:34.534 --> 03:38.265
♪♪

03:38.267 --> 03:39.932
LISTEN.
WHAT HAPPENED?!

03:39.934 --> 03:41.265
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
I'M OKAY.

03:41.267 --> 03:44.565
NO NEED
TO CALL THE POLICE.

03:44.567 --> 03:48.532
BUT, JAMES, THE MAN
CAME TO KILL YOU.

03:48.534 --> 03:52.665
MAE, THERE'S NO NEED
TO CALL THE POLICE.

03:52.667 --> 03:54.732
THE ONLY LAW WE NEED AROUND HERE
IS GOD'S LAW.

03:54.734 --> 03:56.398
DADDY, WHAT HAPPENED?
I'M ALL RIGHT.

03:56.400 --> 03:57.932
I'M ALL RIGHT.

03:57.934 --> 04:00.265
I DON'T CARE
WHAT HE SAYS.

04:00.267 --> 04:04.065
GET A DOCTOR OVER THERE
AND CHECK HIM OUT!

04:04.067 --> 04:06.998
ALL RIGHT, I WILL.
THANKS FOR CALLING, CHARITY.

04:07.000 --> 04:09.132
I LOVE YOU. BYE.

04:09.134 --> 04:11.865
[ BEEP ]
EVERYBODY'S SAFE.

04:11.867 --> 04:15.132
BASIE IS
STILL OUT THERE.

04:15.134 --> 04:19.598
LOOK...CAN WE JUST AGREE THAT
NOW THAT ZORA'S HOME

04:19.600 --> 04:21.265
AND ALL THIS
CRAZINESS IS GOING ON,

04:21.267 --> 04:23.732
THAT WE CAN JUST STOP
TALKING ABOUT DIVORCE?

04:23.734 --> 04:26.798
[ SCOFFS ]

04:26.800 --> 04:30.598
BABY, IT WAS ONE KISS,
ALL RIGHT?

04:30.600 --> 04:33.132
A KISS I REGRET.

04:33.134 --> 04:36.532
I WANT
TO MAKE THIS WORK.

04:36.534 --> 04:37.865
[ SIGHS ]
I DON'T KNOW.

04:37.867 --> 04:39.132
PAPA ALMOST
JUST GOT KILLED!

04:39.134 --> 04:41.198
I CAN'T FIGHT ABOUT
THIS RIGHT NOW!

04:41.200 --> 04:42.865
I'M NOT PACKING
MY BAGS, AM I?

04:42.867 --> 04:44.732
BUT DON'T ASK ME
TO SAY SOMETHING NOW

04:44.734 --> 04:47.465
THAT I DON'T KNOW
TO BE TRUE.

04:47.467 --> 04:50.065
OKAY? I DON'T KNOW.

04:50.067 --> 04:53.598
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

04:53.600 --> 04:55.465
IT'S JOSEPH.

04:55.467 --> 04:58.132
THE ACCOUNTANT
FROM TRIUMPH?

04:58.134 --> 04:59.665
YEAH.
WHY IS HE CALLING?

04:59.667 --> 05:02.532
I DON'T KNOW.

05:02.534 --> 05:05.065
JOSEPH, MY BROTHER.

05:05.067 --> 05:09.365
♪♪

05:09.367 --> 05:11.698
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

05:11.700 --> 05:13.532
WHAT IS IT?

05:13.534 --> 05:16.998
♪♪

05:17.000 --> 05:21.365
SON OF A BITCH
JUST STOLE OUR CHURCH.

05:21.367 --> 05:23.432
[ SIGHS ]
NOW GET SOME REST.

05:23.434 --> 05:26.665
THIS KIND OF STRESS TAKES A TOLL
THAT YOU WON'T SEE COMING.

05:26.667 --> 05:28.698
Mae:
THANK YOU, DOCTOR.

05:28.700 --> 05:30.732
COULD YOU
JUST SHOW HIM OUT?

05:30.734 --> 05:33.998
YES, MA'AM.
THIS WAY.

05:34.000 --> 05:35.731
[ DOOR OPENS ]

05:35.733 --> 05:39.265
[ FOOTSTEPS RETREATING ]

05:39.267 --> 05:43.532
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:43.534 --> 05:45.765
WELL, HE'S RIGHT,
YOU KNOW.

05:45.767 --> 05:47.965
JAMES,
YOU NEED TO REST.

05:47.967 --> 05:49.165
WE HAVE TO TALK FIRST.

05:49.167 --> 05:51.699
BUT FIRST, YOU NEED
TO GO TO PERCY'S...

05:51.701 --> 05:52.965
THIS WON'T WAIT, MAE.

05:52.967 --> 05:56.465
...AND YOU NEED
TO SLEEP, JAMES.

05:56.467 --> 05:58.398
I'M SORRY
I DIDN'T COME TODAY...

05:58.400 --> 06:01.099
TO THE SANCTUARY
TO SEE YOU PREACH.

06:01.101 --> 06:05.432
IT SOUNDS TO ME LIKE MORE THAN
JUST A PREACHER SHOWED UP.

06:05.434 --> 06:09.598
THE WAY THIS BUILDING'S
BEEN BUZZING,

06:09.600 --> 06:12.665
IT SOUNDS LIKE THE SPIRIT
SHOWED UP, TOO, DIDN'T IT?

06:12.667 --> 06:19.332
OOH, LET'S JUST SAY THAT
THE WEATHER COOPERATED, IT DID.

06:19.334 --> 06:21.065
MAE.

06:26.000 --> 06:28.565
THE CHURCH IS YOURS.

06:28.567 --> 06:36.665
♪♪

06:36.667 --> 06:40.531
THANK YOU.

06:40.533 --> 06:43.598
THANK YOU, JAMES.

06:43.600 --> 06:45.732
YOU EARNED IT.

06:45.734 --> 06:50.265
♪♪

06:50.267 --> 06:52.265
OH, MY GOODNESS.

06:52.267 --> 06:54.465
HOW COULD I EVER
THANK YOU?

06:54.467 --> 06:56.399
GOING TO THAT BOARD
MEETING THIS WEEK,

06:56.401 --> 07:00.465
TAKE HOLD OF THAT CHURCH
WITH THE CONFIDENCE OF A SAINT.

07:00.467 --> 07:03.465
THAT'LL BE ALL
THE THANKS I NEED.

07:03.467 --> 07:04.865
BECOME YOURSELF, MAE.

07:04.867 --> 07:06.732
IT'S TIME.

07:06.734 --> 07:10.332
♪♪

07:10.334 --> 07:12.865
MAXINE, I LOVE YOU.
LOVE YOU.

07:12.867 --> 07:14.732
BYE.

07:14.734 --> 07:20.998
♪♪

07:21.000 --> 07:27.065
SEXUAL ABUSE, TAX EVASION,
EMBEZZLEMENT, FRAUD, GUNFIRE.

07:27.067 --> 07:28.998
TELL ME ONE OTHER CHURCH

07:29.000 --> 07:30.632
WHERE THESE ARE
THE THINGS THAT ARE

07:30.634 --> 07:32.465
TALKED ABOUT IN
THE PEWS ON SUNDAY.

07:32.467 --> 07:34.932
NO ONE UNDERSTANDS
MY FAMILY'S FAILURES

07:34.934 --> 07:36.165
MORE THAN I DO.

07:36.167 --> 07:37.398
AND THAT'S WHY
I'M TELLING YOU.

07:37.400 --> 07:39.331
THE DEACON BOARD HAS
ADOPTED A RESOLUTION

07:39.333 --> 07:42.432
TO JOIN HARMONY AND HOPE
MINISTRIES AND MOVE ON.

07:44.801 --> 07:46.832
THESE FOLKS
WANT CHANGE, GRACE.

07:46.834 --> 07:49.398
AND I DON'T BLAME THEM.

07:49.400 --> 07:51.332
MY MOTHER
JUST RAISED THE ROOF.

07:51.334 --> 07:53.632
WHY AREN'T YOU ASKING HER
ABOUT THIS?

07:53.634 --> 07:55.332
YOUR MOTHER SUFFERS
BY ASSOCIATION,

07:55.334 --> 07:58.198
APART FROM MANY
FAULTS OF HER OWN.

07:58.200 --> 08:01.865
AND SHE HAS SOME,
AS YOU KNOW.

08:01.867 --> 08:03.865
SO, WHY ARE YOU
TALKING TO ME?

08:03.867 --> 08:07.132
I'VE OVERSEEN THE ADMISSION
OF OVER 50 INDEPENDENT CHURCHES

08:07.134 --> 08:09.732
INTO THE "H" AND "H"
FAMILY, GRACE.

08:09.734 --> 08:11.998
SOMETIMES IT'S SIMPLE,
SOMETIMES NOT.

08:12.000 --> 08:14.165
BUT WHEN WE HAVE
SOME CONTINUITY,

08:14.167 --> 08:17.899
AT LEAST AT FIRST,
IT'S ALWAYS BETTER.

08:17.901 --> 08:19.232
NOW, CONNIE HAS TOLD
ME SHE'S TALKED TO YOU

08:19.234 --> 08:21.765
IN THE PAST
ABOUT STEPPING UP.

08:21.767 --> 08:23.298
NOW, I KNOW
YOU'VE SAID NO,

08:23.300 --> 08:26.765
BUT IT WOULD JUST BE
FOR A YEAR TO START

08:26.767 --> 08:29.599
UNTIL THINGS SETTLE DOWN.

08:29.601 --> 08:32.332
YOU WANT ME TO TAKE
OVER THE CHURCH.

08:32.334 --> 08:35.532
NOW, I MUST BE
STRAIGHT WITH YOU.

08:35.534 --> 08:38.132
THIS IS HAPPENING
WITH OR WITHOUT YOU.

08:38.134 --> 08:40.798
NOW, WITH
THAT BEING SAID,

08:40.800 --> 08:43.831
WE'D LOVE TO HAVE
YOU ON THE TEAM.

08:43.833 --> 08:46.299
CAN I HAVE A BEAT
TO PRAY ABOUT IT?

08:46.301 --> 08:47.965
OF COURSE.

08:47.967 --> 08:52.065
♪♪

08:55.000 --> 08:59.198
I AM SEEING THE
DEACONS LATER TODAY

08:59.200 --> 09:01.532
TO TELL THEM
THE BIG NEWS.

09:01.534 --> 09:05.198
WANT TO SEE HOW CONNIE
AND THE REST OF THEM TAKE IT.

09:05.200 --> 09:07.799
YEAH...
MAMA, ABOUT THAT.

09:11.600 --> 09:14.265
WHAT?

09:14.267 --> 09:17.799
THE DEACONS WANT
TO JOIN HARMONY AND HOPE,

09:17.801 --> 09:21.398
AND THEY WANT
BISHOP AND YOU...

09:21.400 --> 09:25.832
TO RETIRE
WITH FULL BENEFITS.

09:25.834 --> 09:29.165
HMM. WELL THAT'S
GENEROUS OF THEM.

09:29.167 --> 09:31.532
AND...

09:31.534 --> 09:32.998
THEY WANTED TO KNOW
IF I WOULD TAKE OVER

09:33.000 --> 09:37.465
AS INTERIM HEAD PASTOR
FOR A YEAR.

09:37.467 --> 09:39.665
AND WHAT DID YOU SAY?

09:39.667 --> 09:40.931
I SAID THAT I WOULD
PRAY ABOUT IT.

09:40.933 --> 09:42.898
YEAH, WHEN
"NO" WOULD'VE SUFFICED.

09:42.900 --> 09:44.299
IF I HAD SAID NO,

09:44.301 --> 09:46.099
THEY WOULD HAVE PHIL
RUNNING THIS CHURCH...

09:46.101 --> 09:47.365
OH, GRACE.
...UNTIL THEY FOUND SOMEONE

09:47.367 --> 09:48.632
FROM WHEREVER,
LIKE POUGHKEEPSIE OR --

09:48.634 --> 09:50.131
IS THAT WHAT
YOU WOULD PREFER?

09:50.133 --> 09:52.132
NO, WHAT I WOULD PREFER

09:52.134 --> 09:55.465
IS TO NOT SEE A CHURCH THAT WAS
JUST RESURRECTED BY THE LORD

09:55.467 --> 09:56.665
DRAGGED BACK
TO THE GRAVE!

09:56.667 --> 09:57.798
I DON'T WANT
THAT EITHER!

09:57.800 --> 09:59.732
THAT IS WHY I WANTED
TO TALK TO YOU!

09:59.734 --> 10:02.932
OH, SO YOU COULD TELL ME
THAT YOU DIDN'T SAY NO?

10:02.934 --> 10:04.132
[ SIGHS ]

10:04.134 --> 10:05.865
SO, YOU COULD TRY TO MAKE ME
FEEL SORRY FOR YOU,

10:05.867 --> 10:07.132
THE VICTIM?

10:07.134 --> 10:09.632
SORRY FOR YOU WHO
<i> ALWAYS</i> HAS TO BETRAY ME?

10:09.634 --> 10:12.532
YOU HAVE BEATEN ME DOWN
FOR DECADES

10:12.534 --> 10:14.465
FOR A MISTAKE
THAT<i> YOU</i> MADE!

10:14.467 --> 10:16.132
YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT BETRAYAL?

10:16.134 --> 10:20.565
I DON'T WANT TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT<i> ANYTHING!</i>

10:20.567 --> 10:23.765
"OH, MAMA.
ABOUT THAT, MAMA.

10:23.767 --> 10:26.398
AND, OH, MAMA,
I HAVE THIS ON YOU, MAMA,"

10:26.400 --> 10:28.998
AND "MAMA THIS," AND
"MAMA, YOU DID THAT WRONG."

10:29.000 --> 10:31.865
I'M SICK OF IT!

10:31.867 --> 10:34.265
AARON AND I TOOK
A BLOOD TEST!

10:34.267 --> 10:44.132
♪♪

10:44.134 --> 10:46.332
AND?

10:46.334 --> 10:53.932
♪♪

10:53.934 --> 10:55.865
LIONEL'S MY FATHER.

10:55.867 --> 11:04.832
♪♪

11:04.834 --> 11:09.132
AND WHAT
DO YOU WANT TO DO?

11:09.134 --> 11:11.665
I DON'T KNOW.

11:11.667 --> 11:14.331
I ASSUME YOU WANT
TO TELL BISHOP.

11:14.333 --> 11:16.465
WELL, I DON'T WANT
TO KEEP IT A SECRET.

11:16.467 --> 11:17.732
OH, NO,
OF COURSE YOU DON'T,

11:17.734 --> 11:21.398
BECAUSE WHO WOULD THAT SERVE,
GRACE, JUST EVERYBODY.

11:21.400 --> 11:23.465
♪♪

11:23.467 --> 11:25.132
DO YOU HONESTLY
HAVE NO CONCERN

11:25.134 --> 11:26.665
FOR HOW THIS
AFFECTS ME AT ALL?

11:26.667 --> 11:30.332
AND DO YOU HAVE ANY CONCERN
FOR HOW THIS AFFECTS ME?

11:30.334 --> 11:34.532
YOU HAVE JUST TOLD ME
THAT MY OWN SHAMEFUL MISTAKE

11:34.534 --> 11:36.532
IS GONNA
BE MEMORIALIZED FOREVER!

11:36.534 --> 11:41.998
IN THIS SHAMEFUL, SAD, UGLY...
ANNOYING FACT OF ME!

11:42.000 --> 11:43.732
I AM SO SORRY
I FOUND OUT,

11:43.734 --> 11:45.865
BUT YOU CANNOT ASK ME TO
KEEP WHO I AM A SECRET.

11:45.867 --> 11:48.398
THAT'S NOT FAIR
TO<i> ANYONE.</i>

11:48.400 --> 11:50.465
FINE.

11:50.467 --> 11:52.532
I WILL TELL BISHOP.

11:52.534 --> 11:58.965
♪♪

11:58.967 --> 12:01.498
AND I'M SORRY.

12:01.500 --> 12:03.498
♪♪

12:03.500 --> 12:06.132
AND I'M ASHAMED.

12:06.134 --> 12:11.932
I NEVER MEANT TO BRING...
SO MUCH PAIN TO SO MANY.

12:11.934 --> 12:18.865
♪♪

12:18.867 --> 12:25.898
♪♪

12:25.900 --> 12:28.365
[ CRYING QUIETLY ]

12:28.367 --> 12:32.565
♪♪

12:32.567 --> 12:33.898
[ KNOCK AT DOOR ]

12:33.900 --> 12:35.565
HEY.

12:35.567 --> 12:36.798
HEY, PASTOR GREENLEAF.

12:36.800 --> 12:38.398
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

12:38.400 --> 12:40.332
YOU'RE A SIGHT
FOR SORE EYES.

12:40.334 --> 12:42.098
OH, COME ON IN.

12:42.100 --> 12:45.665
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:45.667 --> 12:47.732
YOU DOING OKAY, POP?

12:47.734 --> 12:50.265
WHAT? OH.
OH, YOU MEAN YESTERDAY.

12:50.267 --> 12:53.132
WELL, NEVER BETTER.
MORE ALIVE, EVEN.

12:53.134 --> 12:54.665
POWERFUL.

12:54.667 --> 12:56.732
MM-HMM. WELL, GOOD.
THAT'S A RELIEF.

12:56.734 --> 12:59.665
EXPECTED NOTHING LESS
COMING FROM YOU.

12:59.667 --> 13:03.865
WELL...THE BOARD HAS ASKED
ME TO LEAVE TRIUMPH

13:03.867 --> 13:06.598
BECAUSE
OF THE SCANDAL.

13:06.600 --> 13:08.399
THEY KNOW IT'S NOT
YOUR FAULT, DON'T THEY?

13:08.401 --> 13:09.665
WELL, THE ACCOUNTANT
HAS TOLD THEM

13:09.667 --> 13:12.665
THAT KERISSA AND I
ARE NOT RESPONSIBLE STEWARDS

13:12.667 --> 13:16.665
OF GOD'S BENEFICENCE.

13:16.667 --> 13:18.765
THE MAJORITY AGREED.

13:18.767 --> 13:20.499
SO, WHAT DO YOU
INTEND TO DO?

13:20.501 --> 13:22.865
FIGURED I'D ASK MAMA
IF SHE NEEDED SOME HELP.

13:22.867 --> 13:24.932
I'M SURE SHE'D LOVE
TO HAVE YOU BACK.

13:24.934 --> 13:27.265
ESPECIALLY NOW THAT YOU'VE BEEN
TRIED BY THE FIRE

13:27.267 --> 13:31.132
AND BECOME QUITE
A STRONG PREACHER YOURSELF.

13:31.134 --> 13:32.798
WHEN HAVE YOU
HEARD ME PREACH?

13:32.800 --> 13:36.398
WHAT DO YOU THINK I WATCH
AT 3:00 A.M. WHEN I CAN'T SLEEP?

13:36.400 --> 13:39.332
MY SON IN THE PULPIT
ON TRIUMPH.ORG.

13:39.334 --> 13:40.765
AND YOU THINK
I'M DOING OKAY?

13:40.767 --> 13:42.498
OH, I STEAL FROM YOU
REGULARLY.

13:42.500 --> 13:45.532
[ BOTH LAUGH ]
REALLY?

13:45.534 --> 13:47.965
COME WITH ME.

13:47.967 --> 13:49.632
WHERE TO?

13:49.634 --> 13:52.698
YOUR MOTHER'S ABOUT TO PUT DOWN
THIS REBELLION IN THE RANKS.

13:52.700 --> 13:55.465
I DON'T WANT TO MISS
THE FIREWORKS.

13:55.467 --> 13:58.165
SO, NOW WHAT EVERYONE
AT ONE TIME SAW

13:58.167 --> 14:00.932
AS IMPLAUSIBLE IS
NOW THE MOST PLAUSIBLE,

14:00.934 --> 14:05.265
INSPIRING,
INEVITABLE CHOICE...

14:05.267 --> 14:06.932
ME.

14:09.767 --> 14:14.698
AND...I HAVE
BISHOP'S SUPPORT.

14:14.700 --> 14:16.898
FIRST LADY, YOU MAKE
A VERY CONVINCING CASE,

14:16.900 --> 14:18.998
BUT IF I MAY --
OH CONNIE, PLEASE.

14:19.000 --> 14:23.765
BUT IF I MAY, I HAVE BEEN
CONFERRING FOR A WHILE

14:23.767 --> 14:25.532
WITH THE DEACONS
AND PHIL DEMARS

14:25.534 --> 14:27.198
OF HARMONY AND HOPE
MINISTRIES --

14:27.200 --> 14:28.831
YES, I KNOW ABOUT THIS.

14:28.833 --> 14:31.132
YOU DO?
YES.

14:31.134 --> 14:33.399
GRACE TOLD ME
THIS VERY MORNING.

14:33.401 --> 14:36.798
THEN WHY WOULD YOU PUT US
THROUGH ALL THIS

14:36.800 --> 14:39.332
WHEN YOU KNOW FULL WELL
WHAT WE HOPE TO DO?

14:39.334 --> 14:42.131
WHAT I NOW KNOW
FULL WELL, CONNIE,

14:42.133 --> 14:44.732
IS THAT YOU HAVE BEEN
CONSPIRING AGAINST ME,

14:44.734 --> 14:49.532
CONSPIRING AGAINST US
LIKE A JUDAS IN A BAD PANTSUIT.

14:49.534 --> 14:51.265
AND IF THE PEOPLE
OF THIS CONGREGATION

14:51.267 --> 14:56.065
EVER LEARNED EXACTLY HOW
YOU CONTRIVE TO BETRAY US,

14:56.067 --> 14:58.332
THEY WOULD LAUNCH YOU
FROM THE ROOF OF THIS CHURCH

14:58.334 --> 14:59.665
IN A WATER CANNON.

14:59.667 --> 15:01.765
SO, YOU CAN JUST GO
AND TELL YOUR LITTLE FRIEND,

15:01.767 --> 15:03.432
PHIL DEMARS,
THAT YOU WERE DRIVING

15:03.434 --> 15:07.465
IN DADDY'S CAR
WITH A FAKE I.D.

15:07.467 --> 15:10.998
MISTY.

15:11.000 --> 15:12.599
FIRST LADY.

15:18.434 --> 15:20.365
OH, SO,
WHAT IS THIS?

15:20.367 --> 15:22.965
A LIST OF GRIEVANCES
DATING BACK TO GENESIS?

15:22.967 --> 15:25.065
IT'S A PETITION.

15:25.067 --> 15:29.365
AS YOU'LL SEE, IT'S BEEN SIGNED
BY OVER 2,000 MEMBERS.

15:29.367 --> 15:31.198
IT CALLS FOR BOTH YOU
AND THE BISHOP

15:31.200 --> 15:33.532
TO RETIRE
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY,

15:33.534 --> 15:37.232
AND IT ALSO CALLS
FOR A CHURCH WIDE REFERENDUM

15:37.234 --> 15:40.299
TO JOIN
HARMONY AND HOPE.

15:40.301 --> 15:42.298
THIS IS HOW
CHURCH WORKS NOW.

15:42.300 --> 15:47.832
SINCE WHEN HAVE EITHER OF YOU
CARED HOW CHURCH WORKS?

15:47.834 --> 15:51.932
YOU TWO HAVE DRAGGED THE FAITH
AND REPUTATION

15:51.934 --> 15:54.332
OF THOUSANDS
OF OUR MEMBERS

15:54.334 --> 15:58.398
THROUGH YOUR OWN MUD
FOR OVER 40 YEARS.

15:58.400 --> 16:00.065
AS CHAIRMAN
OF THIS DEACON BOARD,

16:00.067 --> 16:03.699
I SAY ENOUGH.

16:03.701 --> 16:06.665
IT'S NOTHING
PERSONAL, MAE.

16:06.667 --> 16:10.465
♪♪

16:10.467 --> 16:12.465
[ SCOFFS ]

16:12.467 --> 16:21.065
♪♪

16:21.067 --> 16:23.398
James: YOU CAN SAY WHAT
YOU WANT ABOUT ME.

16:23.400 --> 16:26.932
I'M READY TO ADMIT
IT'S TIME I STEPPED DOWN.

16:26.934 --> 16:28.265
BUT SHE DIDN'T
DESERVE THAT.

16:28.267 --> 16:34.065
BISHOP, FOR THE FIRST TIME
IN THE HISTORY OF THIS CHURCH,

16:34.067 --> 16:37.665
IT'S WHAT THE MEMBERS DESERVE
THAT MATTERS.

16:37.667 --> 16:39.798
AND FROM WHAT I KNOW
OF HARMONY AND HOPE,

16:39.800 --> 16:42.998
I'M SURE
THEY'LL GET IT.

16:43.000 --> 16:44.731
THOSE GRIFTERS SKIM
EVERY DOLLAR THEY CAN

16:44.733 --> 16:48.865
FROM THE CHURCHES
IN THEIR FAMILY.

16:48.867 --> 16:54.732
AND...I WOULDN'T
DOUBT THAT...

16:54.734 --> 16:57.499
CONNIE HERE ISN'T SCHEDULED
TO RECEIVE A CHECK

16:57.501 --> 16:59.765
AS SOON AS THE CONTRACT
IS SIGNED.

16:59.767 --> 17:03.132
BISHOP, YOU CAN FIGHT THIS,
BUT YOU WON'T WIN.

17:03.134 --> 17:06.465
IT IS TIME
FOR A CHANGE.

17:06.467 --> 17:09.332
ON THAT, WE AGREE.

17:09.334 --> 17:12.065
I'LL SEE YOU ALL
IN CHURCH.

17:12.067 --> 17:18.299
♪♪

17:21.467 --> 17:24.332
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

17:24.334 --> 17:27.531
AND THAT I.R.S. LADY
CALLED AGAIN.

17:27.533 --> 17:29.331
I'LL CALL HER BACK
TOMORROW.

17:29.333 --> 17:33.231
I CAN'T TAKE ANY
MORE STATIC TODAY.

17:33.233 --> 17:34.631
YOU KNOW, THAT
DOCTOR WASN'T WRONG.

17:34.633 --> 17:37.532
EVER SINCE YESTERDAY,
I'M FEELING A LITTLE --

17:37.534 --> 17:38.998
I DON'T KNOW.

17:39.000 --> 17:41.232
OH, GOOD.
YOU'RE STILL HERE.

17:51.000 --> 17:53.965
ARE YOU HEADED
OVER TO PERCY'S?

17:53.967 --> 17:57.498
YES. YOU?

17:57.500 --> 17:58.965
WELL, I --

17:58.967 --> 18:01.265
YEAH, I WAS
JUST LEAVING.

18:01.267 --> 18:03.332
YEAH.

18:03.334 --> 18:05.332
QUITE A DAY, HUH?

18:08.167 --> 18:09.965
WHAT?

18:09.967 --> 18:12.632
WOULD YOU LIKE
TO COME OVER FOR DINNER?

18:12.634 --> 18:14.265
I'LL COOK.

18:14.267 --> 18:18.998
♪♪

18:19.000 --> 18:22.832
I'D LOVE THAT.

18:22.834 --> 18:24.998
WHO'S GONNA RUN
CALVARY?

18:25.000 --> 18:26.932
FOR THE TIME BEING,
GIGI.

18:26.934 --> 18:28.865
WELL, WHO'S GONNA BE
HER ASSOCIATE?

18:28.867 --> 18:30.465
I HAVE NO IDEA.

18:30.467 --> 18:31.932
AND WE HAVEN'T
TALKED YET.

18:31.934 --> 18:33.465
IT SHOULD BE YOU,
SHOULDN'T IT?

18:33.467 --> 18:35.732
YOU WERE GONNA ASK
YOUR MOM.

18:35.734 --> 18:37.798
I MEAN,
WHAT'S IN IT FOR YOU?

18:37.800 --> 18:39.365
I'M GONNA NEED
CHILD SUPPORT.

18:39.367 --> 18:41.032
[ LAUGHS ]
OH, THAT'S FUNNY?

18:41.034 --> 18:42.498
LET ME TELL YOU
SOMETHING --

18:42.500 --> 18:43.698
WHETHER WE STAY
MARRIED OR NOT,

18:43.700 --> 18:45.232
I'M STILL THE MOTHER
OF YOUR CHILDREN,

18:45.234 --> 18:48.565
AND I DO HAVE A STAKE
IN WHAT YOU DO AND DON'T.

18:48.567 --> 18:50.365
WELL, I GUESS
THAT'S TRUE.

18:50.367 --> 18:51.565
YEAH, YOU KNOW WHAT?

18:51.567 --> 18:53.299
I TELL YOU WHAT --
FOR THE TIME BEING,

18:53.301 --> 18:55.399
LET'S JUST
STAY TOGETHER.

18:55.401 --> 18:57.065
JUST LIKE THAT?

18:57.067 --> 18:58.432
YES, BECAUSE YOU
ARE NOT GONNA KNOW

18:58.434 --> 19:01.465
HOW TO SEIZE THIS OPPORTUNITY
WITHOUT ME THERE TO GUIDE YOU.

19:01.467 --> 19:02.932
I CAN SEE THAT NOW.

19:02.934 --> 19:04.265
OKAY, SO,
WAIT A MINUTE.

19:04.267 --> 19:05.932
SO, NOW WE'RE
NOT GETTING DIVORCED?

19:05.934 --> 19:10.065
I NEVER SAID THAT WE WERE,
I SAID I DIDN'T KNOW.

19:10.067 --> 19:12.199
NOW I DO.

19:12.201 --> 19:13.665
OKAY THEN.

19:13.667 --> 19:15.632
I MEAN, HOW LONG DO YOU THINK
THAT GIGI'S GONNA LAST

19:15.634 --> 19:17.298
OVER THERE, REALLY?

19:17.300 --> 19:18.798
HOW LONG BEFORE
SHE SAYS SOMETHING,

19:18.800 --> 19:21.598
SHOOTS HER MOUTH OFF,
AND GETS THE HOOK?

19:21.600 --> 19:25.632
AND HARMONY AND HOPE
IS A GIGANTIC DEAL.

19:25.634 --> 19:27.098
BOB WHITMORE,
THE GUY THAT'S IN CHARGE

19:27.100 --> 19:28.365
OF THE WHOLE THING,

19:28.367 --> 19:30.165
HE IS ONE OF THE RICHEST MEN
IN AMERICA.

19:30.167 --> 19:33.932
THIS IS
AN OPPORTUNITY.

19:33.934 --> 19:36.332
IT'S BIGGER
THAN TRIUMPH, EVEN.

19:36.334 --> 19:39.465
♪♪

19:39.467 --> 19:41.532
WHAT ARE YOU
LOOKING AT?

19:41.534 --> 19:43.832
YOU.

19:43.834 --> 19:47.832
WHY ARE YOU
LOOKING AT ME?

19:47.834 --> 19:50.132
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

19:50.134 --> 19:52.065
YEAH, I KNOW.
COME HERE.

19:52.067 --> 19:53.765
NO.
COME HERE, CRAZY.

19:53.767 --> 19:55.298
[ SCOFFS ]
WHAT?

19:55.300 --> 19:57.032
WHAT?

19:57.034 --> 20:00.098
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:00.100 --> 20:00.998
HOW LONG BEFORE
THE KIDS GET HOME?

20:01.000 --> 20:03.599
MM, A LITTLE BIT
OVER AN HOUR.

20:03.601 --> 20:05.499
I DON'T KNOW
WHY YOU ASKIN'.

20:05.501 --> 20:07.299
MM.

20:07.301 --> 20:11.099
♪♪

20:11.101 --> 20:13.365
JACOB.
MM-HMM.

20:13.367 --> 20:14.898
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

20:14.900 --> 20:17.165
OH, NOTHING.

20:17.167 --> 20:18.998
YOU ABOUT TO SEE
WHAT I'M DOING.

20:19.000 --> 20:22.765
[ Chuckling ]
OH, MY GOD. NO. JACOB.

20:22.767 --> 20:32.732
♪♪

20:32.734 --> 20:42.798
♪♪

20:42.800 --> 20:45.465
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

20:45.467 --> 20:47.331
JAMES.

20:47.333 --> 20:49.165
YES, DEAR.

20:52.067 --> 20:55.532
I HAVE TO TELL YOU
SOMETHING.

20:55.534 --> 20:58.798
GOD KNOWS
I DON'T WANT TO.

20:58.800 --> 21:02.998
BUT IF I DON'T, I KNOW
YOU'RE GONNA HEAR IT FROM GRACE.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.398
THIS ABOUT
HARMONY AND HOPE?

21:04.400 --> 21:06.565
I WISH IT WAS.

21:14.734 --> 21:19.399
GRACE...IS
LIONEL'S DAUGHTER.

21:28.200 --> 21:31.099
[ SIGHS ]

21:34.734 --> 21:37.132
WELL, NOW WE'RE EVEN.

21:37.134 --> 21:39.398
♪♪

21:39.400 --> 21:42.332
[ Voice breaking ]
THAT'S IT?

21:42.334 --> 21:43.865
THAT'S ALL YOU
HAVE TO SAY TO ME?

21:43.867 --> 21:46.899
I'M TELLING YOU THE SCARIEST
SECRET IN MY WHOLE LIFE,

21:46.901 --> 21:49.199
AND THAT'S IT?
THAT'S ALL YOU HAVE TO SAY?

21:49.201 --> 21:51.265
BUT IT ISN'T, IS IT?

21:51.267 --> 21:55.532
♪♪

21:55.534 --> 21:57.665
NO.

21:57.667 --> 21:59.998
AND YOU CAN'T
LOSE ME OVER IT.

22:00.000 --> 22:02.798
♪♪

22:02.800 --> 22:04.731
AND YOU ALREADY KICKED ME
OUT THE DOOR.

22:04.733 --> 22:07.132
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

22:07.134 --> 22:09.999
WELL, I GUESS
THAT'S TRUE.

22:10.001 --> 22:12.199
OH, LORD.

22:12.201 --> 22:15.065
SO, WHAT DO YOU
WANT ME TO SAY?

22:15.067 --> 22:24.398
♪♪

22:24.400 --> 22:26.732
WOULD YOU PLEASE...

22:26.734 --> 22:28.598
COME HOME?

22:28.600 --> 22:35.132
♪♪

22:35.134 --> 22:37.699
ON ONE CONDITION.

22:37.701 --> 22:39.699
THIS UNCERTAINTY
AND SHAME THAT YOU FELT

22:39.701 --> 22:42.498
OVER GRACE'S...
LINEAGE.

22:42.500 --> 22:45.032
WHAT ABOUT IT?

22:45.034 --> 22:46.598
THAT'S WHAT SET
YOU SO AGAINST HER

22:46.600 --> 22:48.265
FROM THE DAY
SHE WAS BORN?

22:48.267 --> 22:49.465
I DON'T KNOW.

22:49.467 --> 22:52.832
THAT, AND, OH,
HER STUBBORNNESS, I JUST --

22:52.834 --> 22:55.265
THEN YOU AND YOUR DAUGHTER
ARE MORE ALIKE

22:55.267 --> 22:59.198
THAN YOU WANT TO ADMIT.

22:59.200 --> 23:03.465
WE'RE MILDLY ALIKE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:03.467 --> 23:06.398
SO, HEAL IT.

23:06.400 --> 23:13.232
WOULD YOU SIT WITH HER...
AND HEAL IT, PLEASE?

23:13.234 --> 23:15.765
THERE'S NO USE ME COMING BACK
TO LIVE IN THIS HOUSE

23:15.767 --> 23:19.532
IF WE CAN'T ALL LIVE
AS FAMILY --

23:19.534 --> 23:23.132
REAL FAMILY.

23:23.134 --> 23:25.465
CAN YOU DO THAT?

23:25.467 --> 23:28.932
♪♪

23:28.934 --> 23:32.398
HMM?

23:32.400 --> 23:35.932
YES.

23:35.934 --> 23:39.998
HMM?

23:40.000 --> 23:42.932
YES.

23:42.934 --> 23:44.598
YES.

23:44.600 --> 23:50.932
♪♪

23:54.400 --> 23:55.932
LOOK, BABY, JUST PACK YOUR BAG
AND MEET US THERE.

23:55.934 --> 23:57.865
A PLACE CALLED
WINDSOR AIR CENTER.

23:57.867 --> 24:00.398
ROCHELLE FOUND A GUY
WHO COULD FLY US TO PUERTO RICO,

24:00.400 --> 24:01.865
NO QUESTIONS ASKED.

24:01.867 --> 24:04.998
FROM THERE,
JUST A HOP TO CANCUN.

24:05.000 --> 24:09.965
BASIE, HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU? NO!

24:09.967 --> 24:12.465
JUST STOP CALLING ME,
PLEASE.

24:12.467 --> 24:14.465
WHAT YOU GONNA DO, HUH?

24:14.467 --> 24:16.131
RUN AND GET IT BACK
ON WITH YOUR TEACAKE?

24:16.133 --> 24:18.332
LOOK, JACOB GREENLEAF
DON'T WANT YOU.

24:18.334 --> 24:22.865
BASIE, LOOK -- I CUT
A REALLY GOOD DEAL WITH THE FBI,

24:22.867 --> 24:26.665
AND I WON'T HAVE TO DO ANY TIME.
I CAN'T MESS THAT UP.

24:26.667 --> 24:28.065
WHAT YOU GONNA DO
FOR GREEN?

24:28.067 --> 24:30.565
WE GOT A SUITCASE
FULL OF IT.

24:30.567 --> 24:32.165
YOU NEED TO GIVE
THAT MONEY BACK.

24:32.167 --> 24:33.631
OH COME ON, BABY,
THE LORD GIVETH.

24:33.633 --> 24:34.699
IF HE WANTS IT,
HE COULD TAKE IT AWAY.

24:34.701 --> 24:40.299
OTHERWISE, IT'S STAYING
WITH UNCLE BASIE.

24:40.301 --> 24:41.965
WHY DO YOU WANT ME?

24:41.967 --> 24:46.565
WHY DO YOU THINK?
YOU'RE MY SWEET-ASS GIRL.

24:49.700 --> 24:51.298
BASIE, GOODBYE.

24:51.300 --> 24:53.598
Wait. Wait, baby.
Don't hang up now.

24:53.600 --> 24:55.998
I'M NOT GIVING UP ON YOU.
YOU KNOW THAT, RIGHT?

24:56.000 --> 24:57.865
BUT I DO KNOW WHEN
PRAYER AND FASTING

24:57.867 --> 25:00.932
WORK BETTER THAN BEGGING
AND PLEADING. I KNOW THAT.

25:00.934 --> 25:03.332
[ SIGHS ]

25:03.334 --> 25:04.565
I'M GONNA
SEE YOU AGAIN,

25:04.567 --> 25:07.032
SO I'M JUST GONNA
SAY<i> HASTA LUEGO,</i> HUH?

25:07.034 --> 25:08.098
THAT'S SPANISH FOR --

25:08.100 --> 25:10.565
GOODBYE, BASIE.

25:10.567 --> 25:13.465
[ BEEP ]

25:13.467 --> 25:15.198
EVERY MAN GOT
HIS WOMAN.

25:15.200 --> 25:17.265
I'LL BE DAMNED IF
THAT ANGEL AIN'T MINE.

25:17.267 --> 25:20.332
JUST GONNA TAKE AWHILE
FOR HER TO REMEMBER.

25:20.334 --> 25:22.098
WHAT'S THE DAMAGE?

25:22.100 --> 25:23.965
$40.17.

25:23.967 --> 25:27.132
FABULOUS.
17 IS MY BLESSED NUMBER.

25:27.134 --> 25:29.465
THE LORD GAVE IT TO ME
AT THE ROULETTE TABLE TO USE,

25:29.467 --> 25:31.332
AND IT AIN'T
FAILED ME ONCE.

25:31.334 --> 25:35.598
BLACK 17,
THERE'S YOUR 40.

25:35.600 --> 25:38.398
THANK YOU, BROTHER.

25:38.400 --> 25:40.399
THAT JUST THE MONEY
YOU HAD IN YOUR POCKET?

25:40.401 --> 25:46.299
♪♪

25:46.301 --> 25:49.098
AIN'T THAT SOMETHING.

25:49.100 --> 25:52.231
THAT'S JUST
THE LORD AT WORK.

25:52.233 --> 25:55.498
YOU BETTER GIVE
THIS BROTHER A DISCOUNT.

25:55.500 --> 25:58.032
HE GOT A BLESSING
COMING HIS WAY.

25:58.034 --> 26:05.465
♪♪

26:05.467 --> 26:12.665
♪♪

26:12.667 --> 26:14.465
DRIVE.
YOU GOT MY GIN?

26:14.467 --> 26:17.198
WOMAN, ARE YOU DEAF?
I SAID DRIVE.

26:17.200 --> 26:19.565
[ ENGINE REVVING,
TIRES SCREECHING ]

26:19.567 --> 26:27.365
♪♪

26:27.367 --> 26:30.198
<i> BUT MY RESPECT FOR THE OFFICE</i>
<i> OF THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY</i>

26:30.200 --> 26:31.732
<i> AND THE PEOPLE IT BENEFITS</i>

26:31.734 --> 26:33.598
<i> REQUIRES ME</i>
<i> TO HAND THE REINS OVER</i>

26:33.600 --> 26:34.998
<i> TO SOMEONE WHO CAN</i>
<i> GIVE THE JOB</i>

26:35.000 --> 26:36.132
<i> THEIR UNDIVIDED ATTENTION.</i>

26:36.134 --> 26:37.732
DID YOU HEAR ABOUT
WESTON PRICE?

26:37.734 --> 26:39.298
HOW HE JUST GOT
"ME TOO'D?"

26:39.300 --> 26:41.165
BY A LOT OF WOMEN,
APPARENTLY.

26:41.167 --> 26:42.598
IT'S GOOD
FOR CORALIE, RIGHT?

26:42.600 --> 26:44.432
I DON'T SEE
HOW IT WOULDN'T BE.

26:44.434 --> 26:48.265
I CAN'T IMAGINE THEY'D GET
ANYBODY WORSE TO REPLACE HIM.

26:48.267 --> 26:50.865
SO, DO YOU HAVE
GOOD NEWS FOR ME?

26:50.867 --> 26:52.265
$3 MILLION?

26:52.267 --> 26:55.198
YEAH, THE LAWYER READ THE WILL,
CAME DOWN TO YOUR NAME,

26:55.200 --> 26:57.532
LOOKED AT ME, AND ASKED,
"WHO'S GRACE GREENLEAF?"

26:57.534 --> 26:59.798
WHAT DID
HE LEAVE YOU?

26:59.800 --> 27:02.265
NOTHING.

27:02.267 --> 27:03.698
NOTHING?
AARON, REALLY?

27:03.700 --> 27:05.365
NOT A CENT.

27:05.367 --> 27:07.332
YOU WANT MINE?
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:07.334 --> 27:08.865
I GOT TO SAY --
FEELS REALLY WEIRD

27:08.867 --> 27:10.598
TO CALL IT MINE
'CAUSE IT'S NOT.

27:10.600 --> 27:13.798
NO, HE WOULDN'T GIVE ME
HIS RESPECT OR HIS LOVE.

27:13.800 --> 27:16.732
I DON'T WANT HIS MONEY.

27:16.734 --> 27:20.165
SPOKEN LIKE
A REAL CHRISTIAN.

27:20.167 --> 27:21.432
GETTING TO KNOW YOU
AS A BROTHER

27:21.434 --> 27:23.831
IS WORTH SO MUCH
MORE THAN THIS MONEY.

27:23.833 --> 27:25.765
I'LL TRY
TO EARN THAT FAITH.

27:25.767 --> 27:28.231
YOU DON'T NEED
TO EARN IT.

27:28.233 --> 27:31.898
YOU'RE FAMILY.

27:31.900 --> 27:34.932
GRACE.

27:34.934 --> 27:36.699
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

27:36.701 --> 27:38.299
I'LL BE
IN THE WAITING AREA.

27:41.934 --> 27:43.865
EXCUSE ME.
YEAH.

27:46.467 --> 27:49.332
NORMALLY, THIS KIND OF INTERVIEW
IS A MAKE OR BREAK THING,

27:49.334 --> 27:53.565
BUT, UH, PHIL HAS ALREADY
RAVED TO ME ABOUT YOU,

27:53.567 --> 27:56.998
SO LET ME JUST SAY THAT THERE'S
NO CHURCH IN THE WORLD,

27:57.000 --> 28:00.332
GRACE, PROTESTANT
DENOMINATION, ANYWAY,

28:00.334 --> 28:02.398
LIKE HARMONY AND HOPE.

28:02.400 --> 28:06.798
HUNDREDS OF CHURCHES
IN DOZENS OF COUNTRIES.

28:06.800 --> 28:08.532
PEOPLE FROM
ALL WALKS OF LIFE,

28:08.534 --> 28:13.565
BLACK, BROWN, WHITE, YELLOW,
WHAT HAVE YOU.

28:13.567 --> 28:19.265
WHAT MAKES IT WORK IS
RESPECT FOR GOD'S WORD.

28:19.267 --> 28:23.065
FOR ALL
OF GOD'S PEOPLE.

28:23.067 --> 28:25.065
AND I UNDERSTAND
THAT YOU JUST SIGNED ON

28:25.067 --> 28:28.365
AS INTERIM FOR A YEAR,
CORRECT?

28:28.367 --> 28:30.798
THAT'S CORRECT,
BUT WE STILL HAVE A COUPLE --

28:30.800 --> 28:32.832
ALMOST DONE.

28:35.834 --> 28:38.432
I HEAR
YOU'RE A PROPHET.

28:38.434 --> 28:40.032
[ LAUGHS ]

28:40.034 --> 28:43.465
BOY, THE CHURCH COULD
USE MORE OF THOSE.

28:43.467 --> 28:45.598
BUT WHAT WE'RE GONNA NEED
FROM YOU THIS YEAR,

28:45.600 --> 28:50.065
GRACE, IS YOUR VOICE.

28:50.067 --> 28:54.665
A VOICE THAT CAN UNIFY
THIS CONGREGATION.

28:54.667 --> 28:56.298
A VOICE THAT CAN JOIN --

28:56.300 --> 28:59.832
I ALWAYS FEEL SILLY SAYING IT,
BUT IT'S TRUE,

28:59.834 --> 29:04.598
IN HARMONY AND HOPE
WITH ALL THE OTHER CHURCHES

29:04.600 --> 29:08.198
IN OUR WORLDWIDE
FAMILY OF BELIEVERS.

29:08.200 --> 29:11.598
♪♪

29:11.600 --> 29:16.532
GRACE...ARE YOU READY
TO BE THAT VOICE?

29:16.534 --> 29:22.065
♪♪

29:22.067 --> 29:23.665
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:26.267 --> 29:32.198
♪♪

29:32.200 --> 29:38.198
♪♪

29:38.200 --> 29:41.132
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

29:41.134 --> 29:43.665
GOT A SECOND?

29:43.667 --> 29:47.898
FOR THE SOON-TO-BE PASTOR
OF CALVARY FELLOWSHIP? I BETTER.

29:47.900 --> 29:51.398
I JUST MET WITH BOB WHITMORE,
HEAD OF THE DENOMINATION.

29:51.400 --> 29:53.732
DON'T TRUST HIM.
I DON'T.

29:53.734 --> 29:58.065
YOU HAVE TO THINK OF HARMONY
AS THE...OCCUPYING ARMY.

29:58.067 --> 29:59.932
AS SOON AS CONNIE
AND HER CREW ARE OUT,

29:59.934 --> 30:02.165
THEN YOU CAN GET
BACK TO BEING FREE.

30:02.167 --> 30:04.432
WE. WE CAN GET
BACK TO BEING FREE.

30:04.434 --> 30:07.798
NO, GIGI, I'M DONE.

30:07.800 --> 30:13.065
THIS LAST SEASON OF WOE
HAS COST ME HEAVILY --

30:13.067 --> 30:15.332
PERHAPS MORE HEAVILY
THAN EVEN I REALIZED.

30:15.334 --> 30:19.598
♪♪

30:19.600 --> 30:21.732
[ SIGHS ]

30:21.734 --> 30:24.265
DADDY?
YEAH?

30:24.267 --> 30:27.265
THIS IS GONNA
SOUND STRANGE.

30:27.267 --> 30:30.332
♪♪

30:30.334 --> 30:32.599
WHAT?

30:32.601 --> 30:34.599
I HAVE A --

30:34.601 --> 30:35.865
I'VE COME
INTO SOME MONEY,

30:35.867 --> 30:38.398
AND I WANT YOU TO HAVE IT
TO PAY OFF THE IRS.

30:38.400 --> 30:39.932
MUST BE A LOT OF MONEY.

30:39.934 --> 30:43.599
IT'S A LOT OF MONEY,
AND I DON'T NEED IT.

30:43.601 --> 30:46.799
WHERE'D THIS MONEY
COME FROM, GIGI?

30:46.801 --> 30:49.398
♪♪

30:49.400 --> 30:51.598
JUST SAY THAT YOU'LL
TAKE IT, PLEASE.

30:51.600 --> 30:54.665
I WANT TO HELP, AND I WANT
ALL THIS TROUBLE TO BE DONE.

30:54.667 --> 30:56.431
GIGI.

30:56.433 --> 30:58.265
YEAH.

30:58.267 --> 31:01.465
IN THIS FAMILY,
WE DON'T LIVE BY THE FLESH,

31:01.467 --> 31:04.632
WE LIVE BY THE SPIRIT.

31:04.634 --> 31:07.198
AND IN THE SPIRIT,

31:07.200 --> 31:10.299
YOU ARE MY DAUGHTER.

31:10.301 --> 31:13.032
MY BELOVED DAUGHTER,

31:13.034 --> 31:16.665
AND YOU ALWAYS
WILL BE, HMM?

31:16.667 --> 31:22.465
♪♪

31:22.467 --> 31:24.732
[ Voice breaking ] DADDY.
[ CHUCKLING ]

31:24.734 --> 31:32.965
♪♪

31:32.967 --> 31:36.498
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

31:36.500 --> 31:38.498
[ ORGAN PLAYING ]

31:38.500 --> 31:46.899
♪♪

31:46.901 --> 31:49.232
AS YOU ALL KNOW, I'M SURE,

31:49.234 --> 31:51.765
THIS IS MY LAST
SUNDAY PREACHING.

31:51.767 --> 31:53.298
[ MEMBERS SHOUTING "NO" ]

31:53.300 --> 31:56.532
NEXT WEEK, IT'LL BE
PASTOR GRACE UP HERE,

31:56.534 --> 31:58.932
AND THIS WHOLE RICH
PAGEANT WILL HAVE FALLEN

31:58.934 --> 32:00.798
UNDER THE SHADOW
OF HARMONY AND HOPE,

32:00.800 --> 32:04.332
A FAMILY WE'RE ALL SO PROUD
TO BE JOINING.

32:04.334 --> 32:06.965
[ APPLAUSE ]

32:16.934 --> 32:21.465
I WANT TO TALK TODAY
ABOUT MOSES.

32:21.467 --> 32:27.532
A MAN OF GOD,
BUT NOT WITHOUT FAULTS...

32:27.534 --> 32:30.665
DENIED ENTRANCE TO THE
LAND OF MILK AND HONEY

32:30.667 --> 32:34.665
THAT HE HAD LED HIS PEOPLE TO.

32:34.667 --> 32:42.398
NOW, WHAT HAD MOSES DONE
THAT CAUSED GOD SUCH SORROW

32:42.400 --> 32:45.198
THAT HE MADE MOSES
WATCH FROM A MOUNTAIN

32:45.200 --> 32:48.665
AS HIS PEOPLE
CROSSED THE JORDAN?

32:51.534 --> 32:56.899
A FAILURE TO TRUST IN GOD.

32:59.134 --> 33:05.531
I ALWAYS THOUGHT
THAT MOSES FELT ANGRY, SAD --

33:05.533 --> 33:09.398
LIKE GOD DONE HIM WRONG.

33:09.400 --> 33:12.598
BUT I KNOW TODAY
THAT MOSES FELT PROUD

33:12.600 --> 33:15.932
TO BE ON THAT MOUNTAIN.

33:15.934 --> 33:23.532
BECAUSE EVERY MAN, WOMAN, AND
CHILD THAT CROSSED THAT RIVER,

33:23.534 --> 33:26.265
MOSES KNEW THEM.

33:26.267 --> 33:28.798
HE KNEW THEIR STRUGGLES.

33:28.800 --> 33:32.065
HE KNEW THE STRENGTH
IN EACH OF THEM

33:32.067 --> 33:35.465
THAT EARNED THEM
THAT TICKET TO GLORY.

33:35.467 --> 33:38.399
[ APPLAUSE ]

33:44.201 --> 33:48.799
AND I KNOW HE FELT GRATEFUL.

33:53.934 --> 34:00.065
HE FELT GRATEFUL TO HAVE BEEN
ON THAT ADVENTURE AT ALL.

34:00.067 --> 34:03.065
[ APPLAUSE ]

34:03.067 --> 34:11.599
♪♪

34:11.601 --> 34:20.332
♪♪

34:20.334 --> 34:29.065
♪♪

34:29.067 --> 34:37.665
♪♪

34:37.667 --> 34:46.299
♪♪

34:46.301 --> 34:49.632
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

34:49.634 --> 34:51.732
BISHOP!

34:54.600 --> 34:57.131
-DADDY, WHAT'S THE WRONG?
-WHAT'S THE MATTER?

34:57.133 --> 34:58.865
DADDY?

34:58.867 --> 35:00.598
I THINK IT'S MY HEART.

35:00.600 --> 35:03.165
-GRANDPA!
-CALL 9-1-1.

35:03.167 --> 35:06.332
IT'S NO USE, BABY.

35:06.334 --> 35:08.265
JAMES, WHAT ARE
YOU SAYING?

35:08.267 --> 35:15.598
THE LORD GAVE ME A VISION
ABOUT HOW I WAS GONNA DIE.

35:15.600 --> 35:18.598
THIS IS THE MOMENT.

35:18.600 --> 35:19.998
NO.
NO, IT ISN'T.

35:20.000 --> 35:22.932
DO YOU HEAR ME, JAMES?
IT IS NOT.

35:22.934 --> 35:25.165
I LOVE YOU.

35:25.167 --> 35:27.098
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

35:27.100 --> 35:28.831
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

35:28.833 --> 35:30.765
NO, DON'T.
JAMES, DON'T.

35:30.767 --> 35:31.832
DADDY!

35:31.834 --> 35:34.099
DADDY!
WE LOVE YOU.

35:34.101 --> 35:35.499
DADDY,
DON'T GO!

35:35.501 --> 35:36.932
JAMES.
PLEASE, DADDY.

35:36.934 --> 35:39.532
YOU STAY WITH US.

35:39.534 --> 35:41.899
YOU STAY WITH US.

35:51.534 --> 35:55.798
I LEAVE FOR ONE MONTH, AND
EVERYTHING TURNS UPSIDE DOWN.

35:55.800 --> 35:59.065
YEAH. TURNS OUT
YOU'RE WHAT HOLDS EVERYTHING

35:59.067 --> 36:00.765
TOGETHER
AROUND HERE.

36:00.767 --> 36:03.431
[ CHUCKLES ]
I NEVER DOUBTED IT.

36:03.433 --> 36:05.165
WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO NOW?

36:05.167 --> 36:07.965
[ SIGHS ]
GO TO THERAPY.

36:07.967 --> 36:11.032
TRY AND FIGURE OUT
WHY I WASTED SO MUCH TIME

36:11.034 --> 36:14.998
ON THAT PIECE OF TRASH
BOYFRIEND OF MINE.

36:15.000 --> 36:16.398
GOOD PLAN.

36:16.400 --> 36:19.798
YEAH, THEN I GOT TO TAKE
SOME WHACK SPECIAL CLASSES

36:19.800 --> 36:21.998
SO I CAN GRADUATE
ON TIME.

36:22.000 --> 36:26.932
AND THEN, IF THEY LET ME,
AUDITION FOR MUSICAL.

36:26.934 --> 36:28.332
IN NEW YORK?

36:28.334 --> 36:30.198
YEAH. YOU KNOW
HOW I'M, LIKE,

36:30.200 --> 36:31.865
SUPER CHARMING
AND HILARIOUS.

36:31.867 --> 36:33.265
[ LAUGHS ]

36:33.267 --> 36:35.398
I'M THINKING ABOUT
MAKING IT PAY.

36:35.400 --> 36:37.398
OH, THAT'S AWESOME.
YEAH.

36:37.400 --> 36:38.598
LOOK AT US.

36:38.600 --> 36:40.732
I MEAN,
SOMEBODY LOOK AT US.

36:40.734 --> 36:42.998
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

36:43.000 --> 36:48.265
CAN WE MAKE A DEAL,
THAT NO MATTER WHERE WE GO

36:48.267 --> 36:50.132
OR WHAT WE DO,

36:50.134 --> 36:52.065
WE NEVER STOP TALKING
TO EACH OTHER AGAIN?

36:52.067 --> 36:53.932
DEAL.

36:53.934 --> 36:56.898
♪♪

36:56.900 --> 36:58.298
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
OKAY.

36:58.300 --> 37:04.231
♪♪

37:04.233 --> 37:05.965
THANKS, MOM.

37:05.967 --> 37:07.565
HEY, WHAT ARE
YOU TWO PLOTTING?

37:07.567 --> 37:08.965
HMM?

37:08.967 --> 37:12.132
YOUR BROTHER'S
MOVING BACK HOME.

37:12.134 --> 37:14.532
YEAH?
YEAH.

37:14.534 --> 37:16.732
OKAY. GREAT.

37:19.867 --> 37:21.598
MAY I SPEAK TO YOU
A MOMENT?

37:21.600 --> 37:22.932
UH, SURE.

37:22.934 --> 37:24.265
MARICEL WANTED THESE,
DO YOU...?

37:24.267 --> 37:25.765
OH, YEAH, SURE.
I'LL TAKE THEM.

37:25.767 --> 37:27.732
THANK YOU.

37:30.067 --> 37:33.798
WELL, WHAT'S UP?

37:33.800 --> 37:35.865
WELL, YOUR FATHER
WANTED ME TO TALK TO YOU

37:35.867 --> 37:39.899
TO MAKE THINGS RIGHT
BETWEEN US.

37:39.901 --> 37:41.965
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THAT.
IT'S FINE.

37:41.967 --> 37:44.098
NO, IT'S NOT.

37:44.100 --> 37:47.698
AND I DO.

37:47.700 --> 37:51.132
WELL, IT'S NOT A GOOD TIME
TO TALK THROUGH IT ALL,

37:51.134 --> 37:54.598
BUT FROM HERE
ON OUT, GRACE,

37:54.600 --> 37:56.665
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW

37:56.667 --> 38:00.065
THAT I'M HERE TO HELP.

38:00.067 --> 38:01.932
THANK YOU, MAMA.

38:01.934 --> 38:11.398
♪♪

38:11.400 --> 38:13.332
[ SIGHS ]

38:13.334 --> 38:19.431
♪♪

38:19.433 --> 38:25.365
♪♪

38:25.367 --> 38:27.298
-HI.
-HEY.

38:27.300 --> 38:29.098
NATHAN JOINING US
FOR DINNER?

38:29.100 --> 38:30.598
[ CHUCKLES ] NO.

38:30.600 --> 38:32.965
WE ARE SETTING HIM UP THE
KITCHEN WITH MARICEL AND SONIA.

38:32.967 --> 38:34.765
YEAH, I DON'T THINK
HE'S READY

38:34.767 --> 38:36.265
FOR A REAL GREENLEAF
FAMILY DINNER JUST YET.

38:36.267 --> 38:37.565
-[ CHUCKLES ]
-WHOEVER IS?

38:37.567 --> 38:39.865
YOU READY TO EAT,
LET'S GO, BABY.

38:39.867 --> 38:41.298
LET'S GO.

38:41.300 --> 38:42.532
SO, ARE YOU TWO
READY TO GO PUBLIC

38:42.534 --> 38:45.732
ABOUT BEING HALF-BROTHER
AND SISTER?

38:45.734 --> 38:48.865
OH, NOT TONIGHT.

38:48.867 --> 38:50.065
TONIGHT'S ABOUT
HONORING BISHOP.

38:50.067 --> 38:51.932
MM.

38:51.934 --> 38:54.132
COME ON IN, GUYS.
DINNER'S SERVED.

38:54.134 --> 38:57.599
I TOLD YOU, DON'T GO WANDERING
OFF WITHOUT TELLING ME.

38:57.601 --> 38:59.131
BUT DAD SAID I COULD.

38:59.133 --> 39:01.332
DON'T GIVE ME THE REASONS WHY
YOU<i> DIDN'T</i> OBEY, ZORA,

39:01.334 --> 39:03.198
JUST MAKE ME HAPPY
THAT YOU DID.

39:03.200 --> 39:05.665
YOU GOT ME?
I'M SORRY.

39:05.667 --> 39:08.465
AND YOUR DAD IS NOT
IN CHARGE OF THIS FAMILY, I AM.

39:08.467 --> 39:10.865
YOU TWO EXCHANGE AN E-MAIL,
I GET COPIED.

39:10.867 --> 39:14.865
YES, MA'AM?
YES, MA'AM.

39:14.867 --> 39:18.065
MARICEL, WE CAN TAKE THESE OFF
OF THE TABLE FOR DINNER.

39:18.067 --> 39:20.732
UH, MARICEL KNOWS
WHAT SHE'S DOING.

39:20.734 --> 39:23.699
YOU DON'T HAVE TO HELP,
KERISSA.

39:23.701 --> 39:26.565
OKAY, ALL RIGHT.

39:26.567 --> 39:28.099
THANK YOU.

39:31.200 --> 39:33.198
THANK YOU, SON.

39:33.200 --> 39:42.998
♪♪

39:43.000 --> 39:46.265
IT'S A SHAME I HAD TO BE DROP-
KICKED OUT OF MY OWN CHURCH,

39:46.267 --> 39:48.932
THEN FELLED LIKE A TREE
BY GOD HIMSELF,

39:48.934 --> 39:51.065
AND LAID UP IN A
HOSPITAL BED FOR TWO WEEKS

39:51.067 --> 39:54.398
TO SEE YOU ALL
TOGETHER LIKE THIS...

39:54.400 --> 39:55.732
BUT I'LL TAKE IT.

39:55.734 --> 39:57.631
[ LAUGHTER ]

39:57.633 --> 39:58.665
HOW YOU FEELING, POP?

39:58.667 --> 39:59.999
COULDN'T BE BETTER.

40:00.001 --> 40:04.332
RETIREMENT AND AN ASPIRIN A DAY
SUITS ME JUST FINE.

40:04.334 --> 40:06.532
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:06.534 --> 40:11.065
YOU KNOW, THE LORD GAVE ME
A VISION RECENTLY,

40:11.067 --> 40:14.732
AND I THOUGHT IT WAS A VISION
OF MY LAST DAY ON EARTH,

40:14.734 --> 40:18.065
AND, IN A SENSE, IT WAS

40:18.067 --> 40:21.131
BECAUSE EVER SINCE
I'VE LIVED THROUGH IT,

40:21.133 --> 40:23.465
I FEEL LIKE
I'M IN HEAVEN.

40:23.467 --> 40:30.332
I'VE BEEN GIVEN THAT NEW DAY
HERE WITH ALL OF YOU.

40:30.334 --> 40:32.798
FAMILY.

40:32.800 --> 40:35.599
THIS IS
THE REAL PROMISED LAND.

40:35.601 --> 40:38.031
AMEN.
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:38.033 --> 40:39.732
WE LOVE YOU, POP.

40:39.734 --> 40:41.532
I LOVE YOU BACK.
COME ON.

40:41.534 --> 40:42.798
[ GRUNTS ]

40:42.800 --> 40:51.198
♪♪

40:51.200 --> 40:53.731
GRACE?

40:53.733 --> 40:55.932
WILL YOU
DO THE BLESSING?

40:55.934 --> 41:00.398
♪♪

41:00.400 --> 41:04.398
PASTOR?

41:04.400 --> 41:06.665
I'D BE GLAD TO.

41:06.667 --> 41:08.798
LET US PRAY.

41:08.800 --> 41:11.132
HEAVENLY FATHER,

41:11.134 --> 41:16.332
WE COME HUMBLY BEFORE YOUR
THRONE WITH PRAISE AND THANKS,

41:16.334 --> 41:22.332
AND WE JUST ASK
THAT YOU BLESS THIS FOOD...

41:22.334 --> 41:26.332
THIS FAMILY...

41:26.334 --> 41:30.732
THIS FAITH...

41:30.734 --> 41:36.865
AND WE ASK THAT YOU LET IT GIVE
US STRENGTH AND SUSTENANCE...

41:36.867 --> 41:41.365
♪♪

41:41.367 --> 41:44.099
...SO WE CAN TAKE
BACK WHAT IS OURS.

41:44.101 --> 41:48.765
♪♪

41:48.767 --> 41:51.232
AMEN.

41:51.234 --> 41:53.832
All: AMEN.

41:53.834 --> 42:02.999
♪♪

42:03.001 --> 42:12.132
♪♪

42:12.134 --> 42:21.465
♪♪

42:21.467 --> 42:30.432
♪♪
